1.	Write the title of your project.

Marathon Runner


2.	What is the goal of the game? 

Complete the Marathon


3.	Write a brief story of your game.

John has been training for years to complete his first ever marathon. Help John complete his first marathon by making sure he stays hydrated, and does not get tired. 
John’s goal is to complete the Marathon. The marathon will get harder as the game progresses since John would be tired since he has already ran for a while.
 


 
4.	Which are the playing characters of this game? 
●	Playing characters are the ones who respond to the user based on the input from the user.
●	Cars, monkeys, dinos, wizards, etc., are the playing characters in the game.  

Number	Character Name	What can this character do?
1	          John: 	    You can move him across the marathon track.
