6.	Which are the Non-Playing Characters of this game?
●	Non-Playing characters are the ones that don't have an action or behavior when the user interacts with the game.
●	Hurdles, stones, bananas, coins, etc., are non-playing characters in the game.   

Number	Character Name	What can this character do?
1	        Water Bottle	This character will be displayed across the screen and John will try to collect it. It will help him stay hydrated
2	         Food      	  This character will be displayed across the screen and John will try to collect it. It will help him not be fatiuged 
3	      Hydration Bar	  Shows his hydration level. If the bar runs out he losses the marathon.
4	        Food Bar	    Shows his hunger level. If the bar runs out he losses the marathon.
