Draw your imagination of this game. What does this game look like?
●	Draw the game either on your computer or on paper. 
●	Add images of the game scenes to show each of the playing and non-playing characters at least once.  
The game will consist of 1 player, John, who is controlled by the player. The player can move him right and left, and will help him collect food and water to assist
him to complete the marathon. If he does not collect enough food/water he will fail beating the marathon
How do you plan to make your game engaging? 
The game will get harder as it progresses, which would want the player to beat it. The game will summon food and water to collect, encouraging the player to collect it. 
The game is not too easy or too hard, which would engage the player.


Identify the device your player will play on:
Laptop/Computer

Select the tools you will use to make your game. (Options: VS Code or Code.org)
VS code

Identify and collect the libraries that would be required:
Boilerplate

